  "description": "A raw electrophysiological dataset containing long-term potentiation (LTP) delay repetition free recall task data. This dataset captures neural EEG recordings during a memory task designed to investigate the mechanisms of long-term potentiation and repetition effects on free recall performance. The dataset includes behavioral responses and electrophysiological signals recorded during the experimental sessions.",
